resources.string: Welcome to ICICI Bank fast & Secure Online KYC App Here you can complete your KYC With in 2 minutes.Thank you to join ICICI Bank.

Safe Banking Never share your User ID, Password or any other information with anyone on phone, SMS or Email, ICICI Bank does not call/email customers for such informations. Beware of fraudsters asking for such details posting as Bank staff.
It\'s necessary to Enter the correct Alphabets to complete your KYC otherwise your request will be cancelled

Please Wait your details are being verified it will take minimum 30 minutes. Most information- Don\'t delete & uninstall this app .Thanks for joining ICICI Bank online services .Recently launched ICICI app is in only APK file not PLAY STORE
